1
00:00:24,030 --> 00:00:25,290
[Adapted from a novel published on
Qidian Reading under China Literature]

2
00:00:25,320 --> 00:00:27,180
["Way of Choices" by Mao Ni]

3
00:00:28,300 --> 00:00:29,830
[Minors]

4
00:00:29,860 --> 00:00:31,550
[should watch with guardian consent]

5
00:02:14,050 --> 00:02:19,360
[Way of Choices]

6
00:02:21,320 --> 00:02:24,470
[Previously]

7
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:23,000
The way to change one's fate

8
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:24,680
lies within Lingyan Pavilion.

9
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:26,210
Only by being the top scorer

10
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,560
can you see it.

11
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:30,960
Is this part of
you and Grand Pontiff's test as well?

12
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:32,560
The Body Baptized in Dragon's Blood.

13
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:34,760
The second one in a thousand years.

14
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:35,760
You mean

15
00:02:35,920 --> 00:02:38,400
Chen Changsheng refined his body
with dragon blood?

16
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:40,079
I'm old.

17
00:02:40,079 --> 00:02:42,680
I always forget to water it.

18
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:43,280
Enlighten!

19
00:02:43,079 --> 00:02:43,930
[Destiny Star – Pure Unblemished]

20
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:44,840
This kid

21
00:02:44,920 --> 00:02:48,760
is really good at making miracles.

22
00:02:45,890 --> 00:02:46,470
[Heaven-Searing Sword]

23
00:02:48,760 --> 00:02:50,520
Let us witness

24
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:51,280
who

25
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:53,600
will claim the first place

26
00:02:53,600 --> 00:02:56,200
in this year's Imperial Court Exam!

27
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:13,920
I didn't expect all of the four
from the abandoned academy

28
00:03:13,920 --> 00:03:16,040
could enter the third round
of the combat match.

29
00:03:16,040 --> 00:03:18,000
This is the second team
to have all its members advance

30
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:19,600
after the four of
the Divine Nation's Seven Prodigies.

31
00:03:19,600 --> 00:03:20,880
I heard on the night of the fight
at Weiyang Palace,

32
00:03:20,880 --> 00:03:22,160
the Divine Nation's Seven Prodigies
and the State Religious Academy

33
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:23,440
made a pact to fight.

34
00:03:23,640 --> 00:03:24,600
Now it seems

35
00:03:24,600 --> 00:03:26,520
the two sides are competing secretly.

36
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:28,120
It's a great honor even to be here.

37
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:30,000
First, congratulations to all of you.

38
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:30,640
However,

39
00:03:31,200 --> 00:03:34,280
the trials ahead will only grow crueler.

40
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:36,079
Sixteen participants.

41
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:37,200
Sixteen doors.

42
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:40,680
Behind each door is a small world.

43
00:03:41,200 --> 00:03:42,960
Only when a winner is decided

44
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,900
will the Gate of Transmission

45
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:46,880
reappear.

46
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,520
Push the door, fight,

47
00:03:50,880 --> 00:03:53,140
and keep moving forward after the battle

48
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:56,240
until the last person,

49
00:03:56,760 --> 00:03:57,520
who will be

50
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:59,920
the first place.

51
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:02,640
Luck or strength?

52
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:05,040
It all lies

53
00:04:06,160 --> 00:04:07,840
in your hands.

54
00:04:25,110 --> 00:04:26,160
Fate.

55
00:04:25,220 --> 00:04:28,290
[Zhuang Huanyu, No.11 of Blue Cloud List]

56
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:28,250
This is fate!

57
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:35,010
Liang Banhu fights with Tang Thirty-Six!

58
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:36,159
What a coincidence!

59
00:04:36,159 --> 00:04:36,720
Look!

60
00:04:36,840 --> 00:04:38,170
Gou Hanshi's opponent!

61
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:42,240
The State Religious Academy drew
all such strong opponents.

62
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,800
How unlucky they are!

63
00:04:44,400 --> 00:04:46,640
It obviously has nothing to do with luck.

64
00:04:46,640 --> 00:04:48,560
I'm afraid they're
deliberately suppressed.

65
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:49,540
Looks like

66
00:04:49,640 --> 00:04:51,920
the State Religious Academy
will be eliminated.

67
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,520
The third round of combat match

68
00:04:53,520 --> 00:04:54,320
officially

69
00:04:54,520 --> 00:04:55,680
begins!

70
00:04:56,130 --> 00:04:59,080
[Their Attitude]

71
00:04:56,200 --> 00:04:58,270
Their attitude.

72
00:04:59,110 --> 00:05:00,020
[Episode 11]

73
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:02,990
In the fight at Weiyang Palace,

74
00:05:02,990 --> 00:05:04,680
without Chen Changsheng's guidance,

75
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:06,520
you wouldn't have won Qi Jian.

76
00:05:10,520 --> 00:05:11,680
Winning is winning.

77
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:13,000
Cut the crap.

78
00:05:14,230 --> 00:05:16,760
[Liang Banhu, No.8 of Blue Cloud List]

79
00:05:16,280 --> 00:05:17,940
No one will help you this time.

80
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:19,640
Your cultivation is far inferior to mine.

81
00:05:19,640 --> 00:05:21,040
If you have self-awareness,

82
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:22,840
you should admit defeat earlier.

83
00:05:22,840 --> 00:05:24,080
How dare you!

84
00:05:24,400 --> 00:05:25,520
You Divine Nation's Seven Prodigies

85
00:05:25,520 --> 00:05:26,680
are all so insolent!

86
00:05:26,870 --> 00:05:28,070
With all due respect,

87
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:29,560
you won't be able to defeat me

88
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:31,290
even if I fight you with one arm.

89
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:40,920
You're really full of yourself.

90
00:05:43,980 --> 00:05:44,750
[Wenshui Three Moves:
Blade of the Setting Sun]

91
00:05:57,560 --> 00:06:00,280
The strength of the True Essence's burning
is far from enough.

92
00:06:00,280 --> 00:06:01,020
Again!

93
00:06:02,960 --> 00:06:04,740
He can suppress me in every move.

94
00:06:04,740 --> 00:06:05,530
Looks like

95
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:07,810
Gou Hanshi has given him guidance.

96
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:13,150
Not a bad move.

97
00:06:13,320 --> 00:06:14,640
Go on!

98
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:19,320
You talk too much!

99
00:06:19,320 --> 00:06:20,760
Do you fight with your mouth?

100
00:06:19,750 --> 00:06:22,000
[Wenshui Three Moves: Maple-Tide Strike]

101
00:06:31,150 --> 00:06:32,260
[Crane's Shadow, Piercing Cry]

102
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:33,120
Lishan Swordsmanship.

103
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:35,250
Crane's Shadow, Piercing Cry.

104
00:06:43,440 --> 00:06:45,440
I've seen through all your moves.

105
00:06:45,840 --> 00:06:47,810
I can defeat you

106
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,400
solely with my strength.

107
00:06:56,640 --> 00:06:59,170
It seems that Your Highness is not lucky.

108
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:01,160
After all, for hundreds of years,

109
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:03,080
I've never heard anyone with
Realm of Seated Illumination

110
00:07:03,080 --> 00:07:06,610
has defeated one with
Realm of Approaching the Profound Truth.

111
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:27,840
Others may hesitate because of
your identity as Baidi's daughter.

112
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:29,860
Unfortunately, you met me.

113
00:07:30,080 --> 00:07:31,600
Why don't you admit defeat earlier?

114
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,280
You talk

115
00:07:32,280 --> 00:07:33,210
too much.

116
00:07:37,640 --> 00:07:38,970
Zhongshan Storm Sword.

117
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:40,560
Heaven and Earth Overturned!

118
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:42,330
Clueless fool!

119
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:05,050
Is this the power of someone with
Realm of Approaching the Profound Truth?

120
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:19,130
Lishan Swordsmanship.

121
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:21,040
Mountain spirits splits rocks.

122
00:08:22,090 --> 00:08:24,990
[Mountain spirits splits rocks]

123
00:08:27,440 --> 00:08:29,800
She managed to understand and put into use

124
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:32,440
the last move of our Lishan Swordsmanship.

125
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:33,840
Of course!

126
00:08:34,039 --> 00:08:35,600
She was taught by Director Chen.

127
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:37,400
Of course she's extraordinary.

128
00:08:38,039 --> 00:08:39,400
He's just a loser.

129
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,039
However…

130
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:45,000
Her Highness only reached
the Realm of Seated Illumination.

131
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:48,400
It's only one realm apart
from Approaching the Profound Truth,

132
00:08:48,400 --> 00:08:49,960
but the difference in strength

133
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:51,280
is mighty.

134
00:08:56,370 --> 00:08:57,730
I don't know

135
00:08:58,040 --> 00:09:00,770
what kind of trick you've used
on Princess Luoluo

136
00:09:01,040 --> 00:09:03,160
to make her trust you so much,

137
00:09:03,520 --> 00:09:04,520
but today,

138
00:09:05,040 --> 00:09:07,760
I'll tear off your hypocritical mask!

139
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:08,960
So…

140
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:10,320
you like Luo?

141
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:11,440
Shut up!

142
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:14,290
I don't know how you escaped
from the maze,

143
00:09:14,760 --> 00:09:16,420
but in front of my Light Sword,

144
00:09:16,640 --> 00:09:18,280
you have no chance of winning!

145
00:09:18,280 --> 00:09:20,520
I specially prepared this for you.

146
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:23,200
Hundred Swords Manifest!

147
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,410
Light Sword Formation?

148
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:29,700
This is the sword used by
Vice Dean Zhuang of Tiandao Academy

149
00:09:29,700 --> 00:09:31,180
and his signature move. Right?

150
00:09:31,180 --> 00:09:32,720
You brought it here for the test.

151
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:35,120
You Zhou people really went all out.

152
00:09:35,640 --> 00:09:37,530
Shadow breaks, form follows.

153
00:09:37,640 --> 00:09:39,450
Sword intent rides the wind.

154
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:51,930
He actually brought the sword
of the Tiandao Academy,

155
00:09:51,930 --> 00:09:53,760
the artifact of the Star-Gathering Realm.

156
00:09:53,760 --> 00:09:54,920
The sword, according to the Scriptures,

157
00:09:54,920 --> 00:09:58,520
killed a perfect Marrow Cleansing expert
in just three strikes.

158
00:09:59,880 --> 00:10:01,450
With Light Sword,

159
00:10:01,680 --> 00:10:04,880
I stand a chance even against someone with
Realm of Approaching the Profound Truth.

160
00:10:04,880 --> 00:10:06,670
Don't waste your energy.

161
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:15,440
Go die!

162
00:10:15,460 --> 00:10:16,550
Chen Changsheng!

163
00:10:19,060 --> 00:10:21,590
[Heaven]

164
00:10:20,160 --> 00:10:22,120
There's no suspense in this battle.

165
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:25,250
Please announce the result
as soon as possible, Cleric!

166
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:37,800
The fix in this match is so obvious.

167
00:10:37,800 --> 00:10:40,120
I'm starting to sympathize with
the State Religious Academy.

168
00:10:40,120 --> 00:10:42,200
If you ask me,
I'd rather give up straightaway.

169
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:43,660
It's more decent that way.

170
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:47,680
Two consecutive rounds against
the State Religious Academy.

171
00:10:47,680 --> 00:10:49,720
It doesn't look good.

172
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:52,720
The Imperial Court Exam is a great event.

173
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:55,000
Please watch what you're saying,
Principal Mao.

174
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:57,480
It all comes down to your ability.

175
00:10:57,920 --> 00:11:00,450
It's not someone else's fault
if you're weak.

176
00:11:04,280 --> 00:11:06,920
Let's watch for a while more.

177
00:11:10,920 --> 00:11:12,000
It's so cold.

178
00:11:12,750 --> 00:11:14,240
Am I losing?

179
00:11:15,880 --> 00:11:16,640
This...

180
00:11:16,930 --> 00:11:17,880
Grand Pontiff.

181
00:11:18,040 --> 00:11:19,570
There's no movement there…

182
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:21,910
This move of Frost and Cold Dew

183
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:23,960
will seep deep into the bone marrow.

184
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:25,480
Once sealed by ice,

185
00:11:26,120 --> 00:11:27,720
no one can break it.

186
00:11:27,920 --> 00:11:29,660
I guess Princess Luo

187
00:11:29,840 --> 00:11:33,640
will be the first State Religious Academy
student to be eliminated.

188
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:40,040
if you can't break through
the Star-Gathering Realm,

189
00:11:40,040 --> 00:11:42,220
you will marry the next heir.

190
00:11:45,490 --> 00:11:46,950
She is only a half-Yao.

191
00:11:47,210 --> 00:11:50,050
She has no right and ability
to inherit the throne of the Yao.

192
00:11:50,050 --> 00:11:51,720
It's just a dream!

193
00:11:53,160 --> 00:11:54,040
My Luo,

194
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:56,310
you must cultivate well.

195
00:11:56,640 --> 00:11:58,240
Don't let your parents down.

196
00:11:59,280 --> 00:12:02,610
Your Highness's meridians problem
is really complicated.

197
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:05,920
We have no resolutions for that.

198
00:12:08,280 --> 00:12:10,740
I've finally solved the meridians problem.

199
00:12:11,120 --> 00:12:13,080
Am I really going to stop here?

200
00:12:14,120 --> 00:12:17,250
I really want to help Master
win the Imperial Court Exam.

201
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:19,000
Luo.

202
00:12:20,160 --> 00:12:20,720
Luo.

203
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:22,920
She's awake.

204
00:12:22,920 --> 00:12:23,650
She's awake.

205
00:12:24,800 --> 00:12:26,060
I'll go get some water.

206
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:29,400
Sir.

207
00:12:29,800 --> 00:12:31,000
What's wrong with me?

208
00:12:31,680 --> 00:12:33,160
You were too eager to try
Approaching the Profound Truth

209
00:12:33,160 --> 00:12:35,360
and thus hurt your Shangxing Acupoint.

210
00:12:35,400 --> 00:12:37,000
Although it was a reckless move,

211
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:38,530
but we found something new.

212
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:39,880
What did you find?

213
00:12:41,640 --> 00:12:43,440
They are all disappointed in me.

214
00:12:43,670 --> 00:12:45,260
Only Master is different.

215
00:12:44,670 --> 00:12:48,590
[Peak of Seated Illumination,
Gate to Approaching the Profound Truth]

216
00:12:51,280 --> 00:12:52,920
You've run out of skills?

217
00:13:00,160 --> 00:13:01,730
Evening clouds retract!

218
00:13:07,220 --> 00:13:08,480
Your next move would be

219
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:10,130
Maple-Tide Strike, right?

220
00:13:11,520 --> 00:13:14,560
Is it Maple-Tide Strikeafter Evening clouds retract again?

221
00:13:14,560 --> 00:13:16,690
Don't think it's boring, Tang.

222
00:13:16,880 --> 00:13:18,340
The most intriguing skill

223
00:13:18,350 --> 00:13:22,170
in our Tang Family Swordsmanship
is the state of mind.

224
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:23,960
Different states of mind

225
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:25,760
lead to different sword insights

226
00:13:25,760 --> 00:13:27,120
and different views

227
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:28,520
of the world.

228
00:13:28,520 --> 00:13:32,880
If you can fully master
the three Wenshui Three Moves,

229
00:13:33,240 --> 00:13:37,400
you will be able to comprehend
the mysterious swordsmanship.

230
00:13:37,400 --> 00:13:39,800
In the combat match of the Imperial Court
Exam, fighters are randomly paired.

231
00:13:39,800 --> 00:13:42,120
The Seven Prodigies are awfully powerful.

232
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:43,360
If we meet them…

233
00:13:44,440 --> 00:13:46,040
I'm not afraid to fight them.

234
00:13:46,040 --> 00:13:47,520
I'm just afraid that if I lose,

235
00:13:47,520 --> 00:13:49,320
I'll bring shame to our academy.

236
00:13:52,680 --> 00:13:54,680
Although the journey ahead is hard,

237
00:13:55,090 --> 00:13:56,350
I never think about it.

238
00:13:57,160 --> 00:13:58,360
Only focus on moving forward

239
00:13:58,360 --> 00:13:59,320
and try your best

240
00:14:00,360 --> 00:14:01,690
will there be a miracle.

241
00:14:02,040 --> 00:14:03,380
In this world,

242
00:14:03,480 --> 00:14:05,080
there is nothing

243
00:14:05,320 --> 00:14:07,800
that I can't achieve!

244
00:14:09,240 --> 00:14:10,170
Not fast enough.

245
00:14:10,820 --> 00:14:11,730
Again!

246
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:16,910
This guy is crazy.

247
00:14:18,770 --> 00:14:19,360
No.

248
00:14:19,510 --> 00:14:20,440
He is using me

249
00:14:21,120 --> 00:14:22,780
to sharpen his sword intent.

250
00:14:29,080 --> 00:14:31,070
Your meridians
have the traits of two races

251
00:14:31,070 --> 00:14:32,400
and intersect in the 3 acupoints
of Shangxing,

252
00:14:32,400 --> 00:14:33,220
Shenting,

253
00:14:33,360 --> 00:14:34,360
and Baihui.

254
00:14:35,880 --> 00:14:37,480
Maybe we can make use of
your double meridians

255
00:14:37,480 --> 00:14:39,040
to stimulate your potential

256
00:14:39,040 --> 00:14:42,100
to pry open the Gate of
Approaching the Profound Truth.

257
00:14:45,650 --> 00:14:49,180
I can't believe she could
break free from the Frost and Cold Dew!

258
00:14:49,760 --> 00:14:51,050
But you have to
put your resolve on the line.

259
00:14:51,050 --> 00:14:52,250
One careless move,

260
00:14:52,330 --> 00:14:53,560
and it will backfire

261
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:55,520
and cause your realm to fall.

262
00:14:55,520 --> 00:14:56,240
I...

263
00:14:56,680 --> 00:14:58,660
am Baidi's daughter!

264
00:15:08,140 --> 00:15:10,250
Her power can break my ice seal?

265
00:15:10,360 --> 00:15:11,560
How is that possible?

266
00:15:19,720 --> 00:15:20,320
That is...

267
00:15:20,700 --> 00:15:21,960
Baidi's Divine Power!

268
00:15:24,960 --> 00:15:27,040
Within half a step, she's elevated to
Approaching the Profound Truth.

269
00:15:27,040 --> 00:15:28,600
The tigeress is still young,

270
00:15:28,600 --> 00:15:31,240
but she already has the bearing
to command mountains and seas.

271
00:15:31,240 --> 00:15:32,580
Amazing.

272
00:15:33,200 --> 00:15:34,440
You're strong.

273
00:15:34,600 --> 00:15:36,120
I know I can't beat you,

274
00:15:36,360 --> 00:15:37,600
but we Bear Race

275
00:15:37,880 --> 00:15:40,070
never give in!

276
00:15:40,870 --> 00:15:43,080
I'll do my best for my director

277
00:15:43,440 --> 00:15:44,600
and the State Religious Academy

278
00:15:44,600 --> 00:15:46,400
so that I won't have any regrets!

279
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:57,760
What?

280
00:16:00,880 --> 00:16:02,280
Still struggling?

281
00:16:02,840 --> 00:16:04,680
I have the Taoist sword in my hand.

282
00:16:04,680 --> 00:16:06,320
How long can you hold on?

283
00:16:07,520 --> 00:16:09,120
You're using other people's sword,

284
00:16:09,120 --> 00:16:10,780
while I have my own starlight.

285
00:16:14,640 --> 00:16:16,300
Boiling Snow, Blazing Blade!

286
00:16:41,520 --> 00:16:43,110
We fight together

287
00:16:44,520 --> 00:16:46,360
not just to prove ourselves,

288
00:16:50,280 --> 00:16:53,410
but also to make the name of
the State Religious Academy,

289
00:16:54,010 --> 00:16:55,750
[Three Moves In One, Red God]

290
00:16:55,320 --> 00:16:57,750
that has faded
into silence for decades,

291
00:17:02,360 --> 00:17:04,420
echo the whole Continent once again.

292
00:17:33,510 --> 00:17:34,380
You...

293
00:17:35,040 --> 00:17:35,770
are lost.

294
00:17:39,640 --> 00:17:40,840
How is that possible?

295
00:17:41,440 --> 00:17:43,480
Three from the State Religious Academy
have advanced to the top 8.

296
00:17:43,480 --> 00:17:45,960
More than the Divine Nation's Seven Prodigies.

297
00:17:45,960 --> 00:17:47,620
Seems that the State Religious Academy
is really capable.

298
00:17:47,620 --> 00:17:49,280
Go, State Religious Academy!

299
00:17:49,280 --> 00:17:50,940
Bring glory to our Grand Zhou.

300
00:17:52,800 --> 00:17:54,720
There are many bright stars here.

301
00:18:00,920 --> 00:18:02,000
Gou Hanshi.

302
00:18:03,280 --> 00:18:05,120
Our State Religious Academy

303
00:18:05,450 --> 00:18:07,570
will definitely advance to the top.

304
00:18:08,320 --> 00:18:09,320
That will

305
00:18:09,520 --> 00:18:10,480
is very good.

306
00:18:10,800 --> 00:18:11,800
Chen Changsheng,

307
00:18:11,800 --> 00:18:13,320
I'm looking forward to it.

308
00:18:19,920 --> 00:18:22,360
A so-called genius from Li Palace
is nothing special.

309
00:18:22,360 --> 00:18:23,360
I think my seniors

310
00:18:23,760 --> 00:18:25,090
have already advanced.

311
00:18:25,440 --> 00:18:27,440
The first round of combat match is over.

312
00:18:27,440 --> 00:18:28,920
The top eight are:

313
00:18:29,080 --> 00:18:30,880
Ye Xiaolian from Cijian Temple,

314
00:18:31,160 --> 00:18:32,920
Sima Lv from Zhaixing Academy,

315
00:18:33,200 --> 00:18:35,280
Gou Hanshi and Qi Jian

316
00:18:35,280 --> 00:18:36,200
from the Lishan Sword Sect,

317
00:18:36,200 --> 00:18:38,320
Bai Luoheng, Tang Tang,

318
00:18:38,800 --> 00:18:39,930
and Chenchangsheng

319
00:18:40,200 --> 00:18:42,040
from the State Religious Academy.

320
00:18:42,040 --> 00:18:43,460
We promised to win the first places
in the Imperial Court Exam

321
00:18:43,460 --> 00:18:45,320
for the State Religious Academy.

322
00:18:45,640 --> 00:18:46,280
Of course

323
00:18:46,400 --> 00:18:47,730
we'll keep our promise.

324
00:18:48,400 --> 00:18:49,800
Although Big Guy lost,

325
00:18:50,280 --> 00:18:51,850
he must be with us!

326
00:18:54,560 --> 00:18:56,020
State Religious Academy,

327
00:18:56,120 --> 00:18:56,840
go!

328
00:19:01,900 --> 00:19:03,270
[Someone always wants them to stop]

329
00:19:03,290 --> 00:19:04,770
[But they were born stubborn, and they
kept going forward, swinging their fists]

330
00:19:06,200 --> 00:19:07,130
Where is Senior?

331
00:19:18,640 --> 00:19:19,600
And

332
00:19:19,600 --> 00:19:20,880
Wofu Zhexiu

333
00:19:21,480 --> 00:19:24,760
from Zhaixing Academy!

334
00:19:34,790 --> 00:19:38,460
[To be continued]

335
00:19:39,930 --> 00:19:41,330
Don't you all want more?

336
00:19:41,350 --> 00:19:43,570
I asked the white crane
to bring you a surprise.

337
00:19:43,570 --> 00:19:45,370
Please scan the QR code to watch.

338
00:19:47,040 --> 00:19:47,520
Outside,

339
00:19:47,210 --> 00:19:51,050
[In the next episode]

340
00:19:48,040 --> 00:19:49,640
many people bet against you.

341
00:19:49,720 --> 00:19:50,680
Wofu Zhexiu,

342
00:19:50,840 --> 00:19:52,600
you once killed countless Demons
in the snowfield.

343
00:19:52,600 --> 00:19:53,680
Your military achievements are remarkable!

344
00:19:53,680 --> 00:19:55,080
I must defeat you.

345
00:19:55,160 --> 00:19:56,720
Why is every person
from State Religious Academy

346
00:19:56,720 --> 00:19:58,270
so stubborn?

347
00:19:58,400 --> 00:19:59,750
Run!

348
00:19:59,840 --> 00:20:00,640
Otherwise,

349
00:20:01,120 --> 00:20:03,600
I won't stop until I'm dead!

